| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-4366 — Recovery Inhibition (dispossessor)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: e41597cc-bd41-534e-85a2-a96a3228f103"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
